TS.raw_templates['prefs_notifications_new'] = "{{i18n_ns \"prefs\"}}\n\n<div id=\"global_prefs_container\">\n\t<div class=\"notification_prefs_section\">\n\t\t{{#unless is_mc}}\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_permission_div\">\n\t\t\t{{> prefs_about_notifications}}\n\t\t\t{{#t}}<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">Les notifications de bureau sont actuellement d\u00e9sactiv\u00e9es<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p>Nous vous recommandons fortement de les activer pour rester informer de toute activit\u00e9 importante qui aura lieu dans votre espace de travail Slack.<\/p>{{\/t}}\n\t\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn_success\" id=\"growls_permission_link\"><ts-icon class=\"ts_icon_bell ts_icon_inherit small_right_margin\"><\/ts-icon>{{#t}}Activer les notifications de bureau{{\/t}}<\/a><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_instructions_div\">\n\t\t\t{{> prefs_about_notifications}}\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">{{#t}}Notifications de bureau{{\/t}}<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"alert alert_info\"><i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_info_circle\"><\/i>{{#t}}Cliquez sur <strong>Autoriser<\/strong> dans le pop-up du navigateur pour activer les notifications.{{\/t}}<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_disallowed_div\">\n\t\t\t{{> prefs_about_notifications}}\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">{{#t}}Les notifications de bureau sont d\u00e9sactiv\u00e9es{{\/t}}<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"alert alert_warning\"><i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_warning\"><\/i>{{#t}}Les notifications ne sont pas autoris\u00e9es dans le navigateur. Pour changer cela, ouvrez les pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences du navigateur.{{\/t}}<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_impossible_div\">\n\t\t\t{{> prefs_about_notifications}}\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">{{#t}}Les notifications de bureau sont d\u00e9sactiv\u00e9es{{\/t}}<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"alert alert_warning\"><i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_warning\"><\/i>{{#t}}Votre navigateur ne prend pas en charge les notifications de bureau. <a href=\"\/downloads\" target=\"_blank\">Essayez plut\u00f4t d\u2019utiliser notre application.<\/a>{{\/t}}<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t{{\/unless}}\n\n\t\t<div id=\"growls_allowed_div\" class=\"growls_stuff\">\n\t\t\t{{> prefs_about_notifications}}\n\t\t\t<h4 id=\"prefs_send_notifications_for\" class=\"inline_block\">{{#t}}Me notifier de\u2026{{\/t}}<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"global_notification_block\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"display_flex flex_one\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"small_right_margin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"radio\" name=\"notifications_rd\" value=\"all\" id=\"global_everything\"  data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_send_notifications_for\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"very_small_top_margin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<label for=\"global_everything\"><strong>{{#t}}Tous les nouveaux messages{{\/t}}<\/strong><\/label>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>{{#t}}Vous recevrez une notification pour chaque nouveau message{{\/t}}<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"display_flex align_items_start left_margin small_top_margin\">{{#unless is_mc}}{{prefsNotificationExampleAll}}{{\/unless}}<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"global_notification_block small_top_margin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"display_flex flex_one\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"small_right_margin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"radio\" name=\"notifications_rd\" value=\"mentions\" id=\"global_mentions\"  data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_send_notifications_for\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"very_small_top_margin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<label for=\"global_mentions\"><strong>{{#t}}Messages directs, mentions et mots-cl\u00e9s{{\/t}}<\/strong><\/label>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>{{#t}}Vous recevrez une notification lorsqu\u2019un(e) coll\u00e8gue mentionnera votre nom, vous enverra un message direct ou utilisera<button class=\"btn_link\" data-action=\"your_keywords_jump\">l\u2019un de vos mots-cl\u00e9s<\/button>.{{\/t}}